  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Graphene</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Graphene</application> package provides a thin layer
      of types for graphics libraries.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
